    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "Hey there! Thanks for checking out my car! I\u2019ve absolutely loved driving this beauty, and it's still in really solid shape and ready for its next adventure. It runs like a dream and has been well-cared for, making it a perfect pick if you want something reliable and stylish without the brand-new price tag. It\u2019s been a great companion for me, and I\u2019m sure you\u2019re going to love it! Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
