    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 2006 Porsche Cayman S is a precision-engineered driver\u2019s tool. Powered by the mid-mounted 3.4L M97 boxer-six, the powerplant exhibits robust compression and a characteristic flat-six howl through the rev range. The 6-speed manual transaxle offers crisp synchronization and tactile engagement. Recent preventative maintenance includes a high-flow water pump and a cooling system pressure test to ensure thermal efficiency. The chassis remains taut, utilizing its mid-engine polar moment of inertia to provide exceptional turn-in and communicative steering feedback. Braking performance is anchored by four-piston aluminum monoblock calipers over cross-drilled vented rotors, providing consistent bite and high thermal capacity. While the vehicle shows honest signs of road use, it remains mechanically sorted with a rigid frame and a powertrain that pulls strongly to redline. A superb example for the enthusiast seeking a balanced, analog driving experience.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 35
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Reliable daily driver. Clean title. Well-maintained engine. Interior in solid shape. No mechanical issues. Ready for road.",
      "price": 36500.0,
